Osówko  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Biskupiec, within Nowe Miasto County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  west of Biskupiec,  west of Nowe Miasto Lubawskie, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
